{"type":"message","id":"ba1b7a2d","parentId":"bec0ea89","timestamp":"2026-03-30T00:00:52.246Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n我看到当前目录没有 myquant 工具，但在 TOOLS.md 中提到了有 QMT 量化交易终端在云服务器上。我需要先检查是否有 myquant 相关的脚本，或者看看 scripts 目录下有没有相关工具。\n\n让我检查 scripts 目录和其他可能的地方。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_adc9c2d62ad942d6ba54b237","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find . -name \"*myquant*\" -o -name \"*preopen*\" -o -name \"*plan*\" | head -10"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-customb2","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":1706,"output":99,"cacheRead":41084,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42889,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774828848106}}
