{"type":"message","id":"f1abd88e","parentId":"6408df0b","timestamp":"2026-03-30T00:00:58.067Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n让我查看找到的 batch_preopen.py 脚本，看看它如何工作。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6ca1a0192c54478483a8ce8b","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace-chairong/strategies/backtest/batch_preopen.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-customb2","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":283,"output":55,"cacheRead":42951,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43289,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774828855354}}
{"type":"message","id":"a7f24723","parentId":"f1abd88e","timestamp":"2026-03-30T00:00:58.077Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_6ca1a0192c54478483a8ce8b","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"\n批量回放 MyQuant preopen 历史选股\n用 subprocess 调用 MyQuant（MYQUANT_SKIP_LLM=1 跳过 LLM）\n输出保存到 MyQuant 的 outputs/preopen/YYYYMMDD/\n\n用法:\n    uv run python strategies/backtest/batch_preopen.py --start 20250901 --end 20260328\n    # 后台运行:\n    nohup uv run python strategies/backtest/batch_preopen.py --start 20250901 --end 20260328 > batch.log 2>&1 &\n\"\"\"\n\nimport argparse\nimport subprocess\nimport sys\nimport time\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\nMYQUANT_PYTHON = \"/opt/miniconda3/envs/MyQuant/bin/python\"\nMYQUANT_PROJECT = \"/Users/lynch/Codes/MyQuant\"\nPREOPEN_DIR = Path(MYQUANT_PROJECT) / \"outputs\" / \"preopen\"\n\n\ndef main():\n    parser = argparse.ArgumentParser()\n    parser.add_argument(\"--start\", required=True, help=\"YYYYMMDD\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--end\", required=True, help=\"YYYYMMDD\")\n    args = parser.parse_args()\n\n    # 获取交易日历\n    import tushare as ts\n    ts.set_token(\"4ddbbd10e6e36a7e4d950f5dfcdda7b077769ae287691d8d481bd0c8\")\n    pro = ts.pro_api()\n    df = pro.trade_cal(exchange='SSE', start_date=args.start, end_date=args.end, is_open='1')\n    days = sorted(df['cal_date'].tolist())\n\n    # 跳过已有的\n    to_run = []\n    for d in days:\n        ddir = PREOPEN_DIR / d\n        top_file = ddir / \"top_y5.csv\"\n        regime_file = ddir / \"market_regime.json\"\n        if top_file.exists() and regime_file.exists():\n            continue\n        to_run.append(d)\n\n    print(f\"交易日总数: {len(days)}\")\n    print(f\"已有输出: {len(days) - len(to_run)}\")\n    print(f\"需要运行: {len(to_run)}\")\n\n    if not to_run:\n        print(\"无需运行，所有日期已有输出\")\n        return\n\n    env = {\"MYQUANT_SKIP_LLM\": \"1\", \"PATH\": \"/opt/miniconda3/envs/MyQuant/bin:/usr/bin:/bin\"}\n    # 继承当前环境变量\n    import os\n    full_env = {**os.environ, **env}\n\n    success = 0\n    failed = 0\n    for i, d in enumerate(to_run):\n        print(f\"[{i+1}/{len(to_run)}] {d} ...\", end=\"\", flush=True)\n        t0 = time.time()\n\n        try:\n            result = subprocess.run(\n                [MYQUANT_PYTHON, \"-m\", \"myquant\", \"preopen\", \"--date\", d],\n                cwd=MYQUANT_PROJECT,\n                capture_output=True, text=True,\n                timeout=300,  # 5 分钟超时\n                env=full_env,\n            )\n            elapsed = time.time() - t0\n\n            if result.returncode == 0:\n                # 验证输出\n                ddir = PREOPEN_DIR / d\n                if (ddir / \"top_y5.csv\").exists():\n                    success += 1\n                    print(f\" OK ({elapsed:.1f}s)\")\n                else:\n                    failed += 1\n                    print(f\" WARN: no output ({elapsed:.1f}s)\")\n            else:\n                failed += 1\n                err = result.stderr.strip()[-200:] if result.stderr else \"unknown\"\n                print(f\" FAIL ({elapsed:.1f}s): {err}\")\n\n        except subprocess.TimeoutExpired:\n            failed += 1\n            print(f\" TIMEOUT (>180s)\")\n        except Exception as e:\n            failed += 1\n            print(f\" ERROR: {e}\")\n\n        # Tushare 频率限制：每次 preopen 大约 139 次调用\n        # 200次/分钟 → 每次跑完后等一下\n        if i < len(to_run) - 1:\n            time.sleep(2)\n\n    print(f\"\\n完成: 成功 {success}, 失败 {failed}, 总计 {len(to_run)}\")\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774828858076}}
{"type":"message","id":"fe5c1171","parentId":"a7f24723","timestamp":"2026-03-30T00:01:02.227Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n这个脚本看起来是用来回放历史数据的，不是今天实时运行选股的。我需要找到真正的 myquant preopen 工具。让我检查 MyQuant 项目的位置。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e2a78afa7d5940c69a437021","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la \"/Users/lynch/Codes/MyQuant/\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"MyQuant directory not found\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-customb2","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":949,"output":81,"cacheRead":43288,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44318,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774828858078}}
