{"type":"message","id":"b2e387a6","parentId":"8f34345c","timestamp":"2026-03-30T00:03:41.707Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:da4546e3-8bdd-4291-b88f-472a4b5d4b34 盘前选股+生成plan+上传] 执行每日盘前流程：\n1. 跑 myquant preopen 选股\n2. 读取选股结果 (top_y3.csv, top_y5.csv, market_regime.json, selected_industries.json)\n3. 量化团队分析：决定买哪几只、各买几手、止损止盈比例、理由\n4. 生成 plan.json 并 SCP 上传到云服务器 E:/Quant/strategies/plan.json\n5. 确认上传成功\n注意：\n- 账户用 68039812（模拟盘）\n- 资金限制 10万，单只不超过20%\n- 代码格式严格按 plan.json 模板\n- SCP 用 expect 传密码 Ylz13181849320!\nCurrent time: Monday, March 30th, 2026 — 08:00 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-30 00:00 UTC"}],"timestamp":1774829021706}}
